snippet.title: Astral Throb
snippet.description:
Astral Throb focuses on and curates synthwave soundtracks as a nostalgic homage for the 1980s culture, attempting to capture the era's atmosphere and celebrate it. Note that all materials on this channel are owned by their respective owners. Astral Throb fully stands against art forgery and copyrights infringement. 

Stay safe & microwave

This channel is not eligible for monetization. All ads revenue will go back to the artists.
